{"tid":866963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家樂：下年起不再主動提供膠飲筒","createTime":"2018-10-18T09:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T15:39:07.000Z","uid":101994,"like":1,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"496f4f9b569181bc458b2524143ca471c2e53a99","tid":866963,"uid":101994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T09:35:35.000Z","msg":"連鎖快餐店大家樂今日表示，2019年1月1日起，全線分店將不再主動向顧客提供膠飲管。全線分店亦參與香港海洋公園保育基金的「無飲管運動」，逢星期五實施「無飲管日」。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，全線分店上月起已用木棒，全面代替用於熱飲的膠攪棒及膠匙。目前自助點餐機及手機訂餐程式，亦有提供「自攜餐盒」、「自攜杯」及「走飲管」選項。外賣餐具包亦再沒有加入膠刀，並正研究將現有的膠叉及膠羹改成二合一設計，縮減外賣用品的數量。大家樂預料，實施以上措施後，整體即棄塑膠用量可以減少過半。<br />\n<br />\n大家樂發言人指，集團目前正實行不同方案，尋找符合食物安全衛生，及不會衍生其他環保問題的替代物料，長遠冀望達到不用即棄塑膠餐具的目標。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181018/s00001/1539853214441\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181018%2Fs00001%2F1539853214441&d=kk4ha2SMcNYN79Zc1j76MROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=8bd1bece\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181018%2Fs00001%2F1539853214441&h=805ed8d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181018/s00001/1539853214441</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4578d342b88a21d203dd8451fee5706f17cb7b92","tid":866963,"uid":61280,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T09:42:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">多得偽左膠PR力量，好快返去出街食要自備暖水壼杯筷年代，但餐價照舊！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"11203fcfbedbbb737e5b432c000de999adcca92d","tid":866963,"uid":62668,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T09:43:39.000Z","msg":"以後去大家樂食野唔飲涷飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60913c3a24cba444fb454bb36b316c5fc58f6012","tid":866963,"uid":1374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T09:44:32.000Z","msg":"多撚謝晒啲環保撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"969576f9bfb3cd4c33d6ed574391a14da9e320a2","tid":866963,"uid":193642,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T09:46:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連鎖快餐店大家樂今日表示，2019年1月1日起，全線分店將不再主動向顧客提供膠飲管。全線分店亦參與香港海洋公園保育基金的「無飲管運動」，逢星期五實施「無飲管日」。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，全線分店上月起已<span style=\"color: red;\">用木棒，全面代替用於熱飲的膠攪棒及膠匙</span>。目前自助點餐機及手機訂餐程式，亦有提供「自攜餐盒」、「自攜杯」及「走飲管」選項。外賣餐具包亦再沒有加入膠刀，並正研究將現有的膠叉及膠羹改成二合一設計，縮減外賣用品的數量。大家樂預料，實施以上措施後，整體即棄塑膠用量可以減少過半。<br />\n<br />\n大家樂發言人指，集團目前正實行不同方案，尋找符合食物安全衛生，及不會衍生其他環保問題的替代物料，長遠冀望達到不用即棄塑膠餐具的目標。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181018/s00001/1539853214441\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181018%2Fs00001%2F1539853214441&d=kk4ha2SMcNYN79Zc1j76MROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=8bd1bece\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181018%2Fs00001%2F1539853214441&h=805ed8d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181018/s00001/1539853214441</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face